1
00:00:32,826 --> 00:00:35,600
[Ninja Hattori-Kun is Always Right]

2
00:00:38,583 --> 00:00:40,286
Kenichi

3
00:00:40,981 --> 00:00:41,991
Classmate Yumeko

4
00:00:42,041 --> 00:00:43,108
Tomorrow, you all

5
00:00:43,159 --> 00:00:45,149
are you going to play baseball against the ghost team?

6
00:00:45,200 --> 00:00:45,811
That's right

7
00:00:45,862 --> 00:00:47,700
Yes, I will definitely cheer for you all then

8
00:00:47,740 --> 00:00:48,960
You must try your best

9
00:00:49,290 --> 00:00:51,800
I will go to the stadium no matter what, goodbye

10
00:00:52,389 --> 00:00:53,503
Oh no, that's bad

11
00:00:53,554 --> 00:00:55,725
If I play well, of course I welcome them to watch

12
00:00:55,776 --> 00:00:57,920
The problem is that I play so poorly

13
00:00:58,930 --> 00:01:00,916
Okay, let's practice hard.

14
00:01:06,888 --> 00:01:09,996
Oh no, I'm really playing poorly.

15
00:01:13,158 --> 00:01:14,122
Oh dear, that's strange.

16
00:01:14,173 --> 00:01:16,680
-I clearly saw someone just now
-It's Kin Jai

17
00:01:17,452 --> 00:01:18,888
Is that Ninja Hattori?

18
00:01:18,925 --> 00:01:22,678
My baseball skills are about the same as my ninja magic.

19
00:01:23,393 --> 00:01:24,601
Are they really similar?

20
00:01:24,659 --> 00:01:25,940
Alright, I'll be the pitcher now.

21
00:01:25,991 --> 00:01:27,721
Hit the ball for me to see.

22
00:01:27,772 --> 00:01:30,071
Nin... Ninja!

23
00:01:32,061 --> 00:01:33,698
Why is your posture so weird?

24
00:01:33,749 --> 00:01:34,880
I'm going to throw it

25
00:01:36,680 --> 00:01:37,781
Hold it in...

26
00:01:38,040 --> 00:01:41,398
Oh, that's amazing

27
00:01:42,223 --> 00:01:44,223
Okay, now we're going to practice catching. Put on your glove

28
00:01:44,274 --> 00:01:45,934
I don't need to wear a glove

29
00:01:45,985 --> 00:01:46,922
Okay

30
00:01:48,688 --> 00:01:50,796
Look, I'm going to throw it now

31
00:01:50,935 --> 00:01:53,259
Oops, it's the Earth!

32
00:01:53,310 --> 00:01:58,920
Hold it in…

33
00:01:55,565 --> 00:01:56,752
It's a pinball!

34
00:02:02,530 --> 00:02:03,280
Endure...

35
00:02:04,403 --> 00:02:05,823
Wow, you're amazing, Little Sprite

36
00:02:05,874 --> 00:02:08,188
Please, please be my coach, promise me

37
00:02:08,233 --> 00:02:09,704
Here, Master Little Sprite

38
00:02:09,748 --> 00:02:11,301
I'll kneel and beg you at most

39
00:02:11,359 --> 00:02:12,687
Here, please by tomorrow

40
00:02:12,738 --> 00:02:14,545
Make me a baseball player

41
00:02:14,576 --> 00:02:17,215
Huh? You want to become a good player in a day?

42
00:02:18,716 --> 00:02:21,332
Kenji, look at what these are.

43
00:02:21,450 --> 00:02:22,479
Are these red beans?

44
00:02:22,530 --> 00:02:23,666
That's right

45
00:02:23,717 --> 00:02:25,668
-Are you trying to make red bean soup?
-No

46
00:02:25,711 --> 00:02:27,579
I mean when I practice my swordsmanship

47
00:02:27,630 --> 00:02:30,216
You have to concentrate and stare at the red bean

48
00:02:30,515 --> 00:02:31,604
It's very strange

49
00:02:31,655 --> 00:02:33,802
When you stare at the bean for a long time

50
00:02:33,853 --> 00:02:36,390
That bean will naturally get bigger

51
00:02:36,441 --> 00:02:38,040
And then

52
00:02:38,735 --> 00:02:40,579
Whether it's red beans or rice

53
00:02:40,630 --> 00:02:42,680
It can be cut in half immediately.

54
00:02:43,156 --> 00:02:44,680
As big as a baseball.

55
00:02:44,731 --> 00:02:47,061
It should be easy to hit, right?

56
00:02:47,375 --> 00:02:49,017
That makes a lot of sense.

57
00:02:49,710 --> 00:02:50,850
Okay.

58
00:02:51,014 --> 00:02:52,171
Sigh, since it's like that...

59
00:02:52,228 --> 00:02:55,601
I won't sleep tonight no matter what. I have to stare at the red bean all night.

60
00:03:04,685 --> 00:03:07,591
Why doesn't the red bean get bigger no matter how much I stare at it?

61
00:03:07,642 --> 00:03:10,505
It's very simple, because your skills aren't good enough.

62
00:03:14,046 --> 00:03:15,621
Oh no, this is bad...

63
00:03:15,672 --> 00:03:18,195
Oh no, of course I fell asleep last night without realizing it.

64
00:03:18,246 --> 00:03:19,948
The... the red bean, oh no.

65
00:03:19,999 --> 00:03:23,419
- Oh no, it looks really big.
- Then what about this baseball?

66
00:03:28,236 --> 00:03:29,971
It looks quite big.

67
00:03:30,022 --> 00:03:32,342
It looks bigger, which means you...

68
00:03:32,373 --> 00:03:34,570
Oh no, I finally succeeded.

69
00:03:34,621 --> 00:03:35,720
Oh no, this is really too much.

70
00:03:35,884 --> 00:03:37,657
Little clever one, thank you so much.

71
00:03:37,708 --> 00:03:40,415
Today I will definitely... hiss, I can be the star of the show.

72
00:03:40,606 --> 00:03:43,095
Jian Zai, why aren't you up yet at this hour?

73
00:03:43,173 --> 00:03:45,553
Oh dear, it's already 8 o'clock, eh?

74
00:03:47,509 --> 00:03:49,349
Oh dear, why is it such a big red bean?

75
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:50,713
How did you get it?

76
00:03:51,066 --> 00:03:53,557
Oh, so Mommy can also see it's a big one?

77
00:03:53,716 --> 00:03:56,552
Oh dear, so it's an artificial red bean?

78
00:03:56,603 --> 00:03:57,893
I understand now, you little imp

79
00:03:57,943 --> 00:03:59,666
You want to make me full of confidence, don't you?

80
00:04:00,095 --> 00:04:01,900
Hold on...

81
00:04:03,304 --> 00:04:04,640
Kin Zai!

82
00:04:05,145 --> 00:04:07,492
Oh dear, Mommy, please tell him I have a cold

83
00:04:07,543 --> 00:04:09,640
I can't participate in the competition, oh no.

84
00:04:10,350 --> 00:04:12,810
Everyone, I am truly very sorry.

85
00:04:13,062 --> 00:04:14,179
Endure...

86
00:04:20,006 --> 00:04:20,993
It's Kin Jai.

87
00:04:21,044 --> 00:04:23,175
You have a cold and are still participating in the competition?

88
00:04:28,643 --> 00:04:30,053
Missed three times.

89
00:04:30,104 --> 00:04:32,510
Eight people in a row have already been eliminated by missing.

90
00:04:32,550 --> 00:04:34,805
Oh no, next is Kin Jai.

91
00:04:34,856 --> 00:04:36,883
Kin Jai, you have to keep going!

92
00:04:39,216 --> 00:04:40,701
It's Kin Jai's turn to appear.

93
00:04:40,752 --> 00:04:42,422
He wins less than he loses

94
00:04:42,983 --> 00:04:44,583
His pose is so weird

95
00:04:46,774 --> 00:04:48,510
No wonder Kin Zai knows he can't hit it three times

96
00:04:48,593 --> 00:04:50,707
So he just went wild

97
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:57,417
Well done, it's a home run

98
00:04:57,475 --> 00:04:59,450
Wow, amazing

99
00:05:03,702 --> 00:05:06,297
Ouch... why... why is it like this?

100
00:05:07,956 --> 00:05:10,709
-Wow, well done!
-Come on Kin Zai, come on!

101
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:12,412
Endure...

102
00:05:13,172 --> 00:05:14,968
Well done Kin Zai

103
00:05:17,232 --> 00:05:19,960
Oh no, what happened? Oh no...

104
00:05:20,658 --> 00:05:22,728
Eh... aren't these my jerseys?

105
00:05:22,779 --> 00:05:23,952
Who is it, really?

106
00:05:24,003 --> 00:05:26,775
- It's Kin Zai...
- It's Kin Zai...

107
00:05:26,826 --> 00:05:28,240
Let's put it on first

108
00:05:29,045 --> 00:05:31,028
Kin Zai, where have you been?

109
00:05:31,079 --> 00:05:32,392
It's your turn to play now

110
00:05:32,443 --> 00:05:34,019
We'll definitely win if we just get one more point

111
00:05:34,070 --> 00:05:35,424
Kin Zai, you need to try harder

112
00:05:35,475 --> 00:05:37,349
Oh no, why is it down to the wire

113
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:39,371
- It's my turn already?
- One, two, three, three, two, one

114
00:05:39,422 --> 00:05:41,400
Kin Jai will definitely make it

115
00:05:42,101 --> 00:05:43,720
Oh no, we've lost all face anyway

116
00:05:43,771 --> 00:05:45,304
Might as well go crazy

117
00:05:47,135 --> 00:05:51,205
Why is Kin Jai playing again?
He's my nemesis today

118
00:05:55,126 --> 00:05:57,508
Oh no, the ball is too fast, I can't hit it

119
00:05:55,512 --> 00:05:55,126
Great shot

120
00:05:57,562 --> 00:06:00,261
Oh no, he totally doesn't take me seriously

121
00:06:00,312 --> 00:06:01,605
How can this be?

122
00:06:05,964 --> 00:06:06,819
Well done

123
00:06:06,870 --> 00:06:09,013
Great! Our team won!

124
00:06:09,243 --> 00:06:12,306
Great! We only won today thanks to you!

125
00:06:12,357 --> 00:06:15,590
Kin Jai, you're really great, Kin Jai

126
00:06:15,796 --> 00:06:17,491
No, I was just...

127
00:06:17,541 --> 00:06:20,283
You don't have to be so humble, you definitely held something back

128
00:06:20,340 --> 00:06:22,513
- You're great
- You're really amazing

129
00:06:23,250 --> 00:06:25,392
A little trick was all it took to get it done

130
00:06:28,270 --> 00:06:31,310
[Transfer student from Kōka]

131
00:06:36,703 --> 00:06:37,453
Classmates

132
00:06:37,504 --> 00:06:40,717
This is our new classmate, Jin Mak-kei, who just transferred to our school

133
00:06:41,297 --> 00:06:43,400
Please give me your guidance.

134
00:06:43,796 --> 00:06:46,750
He looks quite honest.

135
00:06:52,063 --> 00:06:55,210
Hey... do you want to play baseball with us?

136
00:06:55,261 --> 00:06:56,760
Oh, I don't know how to play.

137
00:06:57,594 --> 00:06:59,396
He looks like a woman.

138
00:06:59,453 --> 00:07:00,560
Be careful!

139
00:07:02,607 --> 00:07:04,057
Hey, I'll catch it.

140
00:07:05,583 --> 00:07:07,210
You're so good at catching balls?

141
00:07:07,261 --> 00:07:08,656
It was just luck.

142
00:07:08,707 --> 00:07:09,581
Really?

143
00:07:10,485 --> 00:07:12,178
Yes, Classmate Golden Mak Kai

144
00:07:12,228 --> 00:07:13,509
What? You know how to embroider?

145
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:15,069
Yes… Yes, Classmate Yau Mei

146
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,745
Wow, that's beautiful

147
00:07:16,795 --> 00:07:18,640
If you like it, I'll give it to you

148
00:07:18,873 --> 00:07:20,523
Really? You're giving it to me?

149
00:07:20,573 --> 00:07:21,415
Thank you

150
00:07:26,276 --> 00:07:29,079
Kin Jai, Golden Mak Kai's handicraft is really good

151
00:07:29,104 --> 00:07:30,396
It's passable, I guess

152
00:07:30,447 --> 00:07:32,465
Oh no, what should I do?

153
00:07:32,516 --> 00:07:35,950
I'm wearing my new shoes today, so I don't want to get them wet.

154
00:07:38,303 --> 00:07:41,160
Look, if you step over my schoolbag, they won't get wet.

155
00:07:41,457 --> 00:07:43,265
Oh dear, this person is not only pretentious

156
00:07:43,316 --> 00:07:44,920
-…but also hypocritical
-You're too kind.

157
00:07:45,272 --> 00:07:46,400
What are you thanking me for?

158
00:07:47,697 --> 00:07:49,003
Thank you so much.

159
00:07:49,054 --> 00:07:50,541
You're really too kind.

160
00:07:50,592 --> 00:07:52,920
You're welcome, it's my duty.

161
00:07:58,664 --> 00:08:00,566
Alright, classmate King Mak-kai, goodbye.

162
00:08:00,623 --> 00:08:01,519
See you tomorrow morning.

163
00:08:01,570 --> 00:08:02,586
Oh no, why are you doing this?

164
00:08:02,637 --> 00:08:04,710
He... he didn't say 'goodbye' to me?

165
00:08:07,384 --> 00:08:07,790
Oh no!

166
00:08:07,841 --> 00:08:09,768
Why did you suddenly change into a different person?

167
00:08:09,819 --> 00:08:12,061
I have a split personality, so it's not strange at all.

168
00:08:12,112 --> 00:08:13,568
Your tone of voice has become fierce.

169
00:08:13,618 --> 00:08:15,072
Come on, give me a massage.

170
00:08:15,625 --> 00:08:16,548
You should be joking.

171
00:08:16,592 --> 00:08:19,019
For no reason, why do you want me to give you a massage?

172
00:08:19,070 --> 00:08:20,470
Fine, you're not giving me a massage.

173
00:08:20,520 --> 00:08:21,506
I will give you a massage

174
00:08:21,812 --> 00:08:23,440
Don't squeeze me

175
00:08:24,975 --> 00:08:26,555
Behave yourself

176
00:08:29,679 --> 00:08:30,760
The teacher is coming

177
00:08:31,205 --> 00:08:32,633
Oh, switch positions

178
00:08:35,172 --> 00:08:37,202
What are you two doing?

179
00:08:37,253 --> 00:08:38,116
Eh... like this

180
00:08:38,173 --> 00:08:40,696
Because Ken's classmate takes good care of me in all aspects

181
00:08:40,747 --> 00:08:42,922
So I'm giving him a massage

182
00:08:42,973 --> 00:08:43,972
Hey, Ken

183
00:08:44,029 --> 00:08:46,063
Why would you want a classmate to act like this?

184
00:08:46,239 --> 00:08:47,749
Teacher, I didn't.

185
00:08:47,809 --> 00:08:49,269
You're not allowed to say that.

186
00:08:51,039 --> 00:08:52,306
Don't you know your responsibility is to

187
00:08:52,357 --> 00:08:54,323
guide the transfer students?

188
00:08:57,265 --> 00:08:58,628
That was really fun just now.

189
00:08:58,691 --> 00:09:01,370
I don't think it was fun at all, I'm leaving.

190
00:09:01,815 --> 00:09:02,748
Hey, wait a moment.

191
00:09:02,799 --> 00:09:04,400
I'll grace your place with a visit.

192
00:09:06,325 --> 00:09:07,834
I'm back.

193
00:09:07,885 --> 00:09:09,200
Son, you're back?

194
00:09:09,691 --> 00:09:11,945
Mom, this is my classmate Kim Mak-kei

195
00:09:12,105 --> 00:09:13,870
Sorry to bother you

196
00:09:14,899 --> 00:09:16,103
I am truly very envious

197
00:09:16,159 --> 00:09:18,219
Kin-zai, you have such a gentle and beautiful sister

198
00:09:18,270 --> 00:09:20,185
Oops, she's not my sister, she's my mommy

199
00:09:20,236 --> 00:09:21,943
Oh really?

200
00:09:22,176 --> 00:09:24,823
Do I really look that young?

201
00:09:25,643 --> 00:09:27,329
Look, this is my room

202
00:09:28,284 --> 00:09:29,928
Oops, what are you doing?

203
00:09:25,643 --> 00:09:27,329
This is my room.

204
00:09:28,284 --> 00:09:29,928
Hey, what are you doing?

205
00:09:35,721 --> 00:09:36,440
You go in first!

206
00:09:38,188 --> 00:09:39,096
Where is it now?

207
00:09:40,013 --> 00:09:41,560
That's right, it's here.

208
00:09:41,950 --> 00:09:44,989
Iga ninja, watch out, come out!

209
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:49,725
Ow, bear it!

210
00:09:51,623 --> 00:09:53,013
Oh no, don't...

211
00:09:53,186 --> 00:09:54,040
Don't do that.

212
00:09:54,868 --> 00:09:55,632
Watch out!

213
00:10:09,708 --> 00:10:12,178
Kin-zai, what are you guys doing in the room?

214
00:10:12,229 --> 00:10:13,490
Oh no, don't hit anymore

215
00:10:13,540 --> 00:10:15,399
Stop it, Mom is coming!

216
00:10:17,094 --> 00:10:18,724
Look at this move, smoke screen!

217
00:10:18,781 --> 00:10:21,419
Oh no, why is there so much smoke in the room? What are you doing?

218
00:10:22,305 --> 00:10:25,479
- What happened to you, classmate Golden麦基?
- A strange younger brother bullied me

219
00:10:25,530 --> 00:10:26,955
Oh no, is it the little spirit?

220
00:10:27,006 --> 00:10:28,315
Endure...

221
00:10:30,557 --> 00:10:31,499
How can this be?

222
00:10:31,550 --> 00:10:34,132
How can you bully such an honest child?

223
00:10:34,183 --> 00:10:35,783
Oh, Mother, I didn't bully him

224
00:10:35,834 --> 00:10:38,227
As a punishment, you are not allowed to have dim sum

225
00:10:38,787 --> 00:10:41,120
Auntie, please forgive them

226
00:10:41,571 --> 00:10:42,564
Because I am here

227
00:10:42,615 --> 00:10:43,884
They are my first pair of friends

228
00:10:43,934 --> 00:10:45,125
I can't bear to leave them

229
00:10:45,175 --> 00:10:46,483
You are so hypocritical

230
00:10:46,534 --> 00:10:47,856
Back in school

231
00:10:47,913 --> 00:10:49,910
Because I was too honest and too kind

232
00:10:49,961 --> 00:10:51,638
No one wanted to be friends with me

233
00:10:51,689 --> 00:10:54,222
This makes me so lonely

234
00:10:54,272 --> 00:10:55,989
Oh, how pathetic

235
00:10:56,039 --> 00:10:56,704
Jian Zai

236
00:10:56,755 --> 00:10:58,744
I want you to be good friends with classmate Jin Mai Ji

237
00:10:58,795 --> 00:11:00,108
Remember that

238
00:11:03,628 --> 00:11:06,809
Oh, who on earth is that Jin Mai Ji?

239
00:11:06,860 --> 00:11:09,523
He is a ninja from the Kōka school

240
00:11:09,573 --> 00:11:12,014
Our Iga school and Kōka school ninjas

241
00:11:12,064 --> 00:11:13,112
are mortal enemies

242
00:11:13,163 --> 00:11:13,870
No wonder

243
00:11:13,933 --> 00:11:15,493
When they saw you just now,

244
00:11:15,544 --> 00:11:17,126
they were practically blinded by rage.

245
00:11:20,651 --> 00:11:23,071
Hey, I haven't settled the score with you for yesterday yet!

246
00:11:23,123 --> 00:11:25,512
I challenge the Iga ninja from your house to a duel!

247
00:11:25,563 --> 00:11:27,938
Dueling is a barbaric act, why must you do this?

248
00:11:27,989 --> 00:11:29,224
-Why not just be friends?
-Hmph, you scoundrel!

249
00:11:29,275 --> 00:11:31,360
Do you want me to hit you again?

250
00:11:35,432 --> 00:11:37,521
So the Iga ninja was hiding here, was he?

251
00:11:37,586 --> 00:11:39,802
That's right, in order to protect me,

252
00:11:39,853 --> 00:11:41,219
she always accompanies me to school.

253
00:11:41,270 --> 00:11:43,600
This is great, let's duel here

254
00:11:44,219 --> 00:11:46,460
This is a school, how can we duel here?

255
00:11:46,511 --> 00:11:47,546
Take this!

256
00:11:48,317 --> 00:11:50,130
No, don't do this you guys

257
00:11:50,181 --> 00:11:51,800
Stop fighting, hey, stop it

258
00:11:51,851 --> 00:11:53,640
What's all the noise about?

259
00:11:57,463 --> 00:11:58,313
Kin Jai

260
00:11:58,376 --> 00:11:59,745
You called classmate Kam Mak Kai again today

261
00:11:59,795 --> 00:12:01,408
To give you a massage, is that it?

262
00:12:01,856 --> 00:12:03,003
There's no such thing

263
00:12:03,054 --> 00:12:04,880
Student Kam Mak-kei, come here

264
00:12:07,496 --> 00:12:09,195
Oh no, where did it go?

265
00:12:09,245 --> 00:12:11,044
Where did student Kam Mak-kei go?

266
00:12:11,825 --> 00:12:12,946
Hey, Kin-zai

267
00:12:13,002 --> 00:12:14,132
How dare you!

268
00:12:14,183 --> 00:12:15,336
To actually play a trick on the teacher

269
00:12:15,388 --> 00:12:16,452
No, I didn't

270
00:12:16,503 --> 00:12:18,331
It has nothing to do with me at all

271
00:12:18,476 --> 00:12:20,666
In the end, I'll be mad at the teacher again

272
00:12:20,717 --> 00:12:22,872
We'll settle this another day

273
00:12:25,705 --> 00:12:28,707
Little Ling-lung comes to pay respects.

274
00:12:49,264 --> 00:12:50,626
Hey... wait a moment, kid.

275
00:12:50,677 --> 00:12:52,584
Hey, give me the bus fare, the bus fare.

276
00:12:52,771 --> 00:12:53,690
Look.

277
00:12:53,741 --> 00:12:54,534
Oh no!

278
00:12:56,757 --> 00:12:58,641
Hey, wait a minute...

279
00:12:58,691 --> 00:13:01,204
Hey, bus fare, you haven't given me the bus fare yet.

280
00:13:12,350 --> 00:13:14,403
This move is called smoke screen.

281
00:13:18,232 --> 00:13:19,772
Alright, what's going on?

282
00:13:19,823 --> 00:13:21,300
Look up there.

283
00:13:22,272 --> 00:13:23,649
Hey, hey, kid, you're in danger.

284
00:13:23,700 --> 00:13:24,589
Stay right there and don't move.

285
00:13:24,640 --> 00:13:25,561
I'm coming to save you now.

286
00:13:32,071 --> 00:13:33,560
That's all for now.

287
00:13:33,611 --> 00:13:35,919
Hey, no, don't jump!

288
00:13:35,970 --> 00:13:37,520
Oh no, don't jump!
Oh no, it's dangerous.

289
00:13:41,247 --> 00:13:42,663
Oh no, this is really bad.

290
00:13:42,714 --> 00:13:44,884
I have a fear of heights.

291
00:13:52,264 --> 00:13:53,824
Kin Jai and Siu Ling Jing.

292
00:13:53,875 --> 00:13:54,944
Where have they gone now?

293
00:13:55,310 --> 00:13:56,890
They've gone out to play

294
00:13:56,941 --> 00:13:59,224
Oh, no wonder the house is so quiet

295
00:14:04,693 --> 00:14:07,386
Oh dear, I'm so tired, let me sit down first

296
00:14:11,906 --> 00:14:12,973
It's delicious

297
00:14:13,346 --> 00:14:15,660
Hey, Xiao Lu, who are you?

298
00:14:16,966 --> 00:14:18,817
Oh dear, where is it?

299
00:14:19,490 --> 00:14:21,096
Huh? What are you looking for?

300
00:14:21,397 --> 00:14:22,677
Of course it's upstairs

301
00:14:23,196 --> 00:14:24,250
Upstairs?

302
00:14:27,017 --> 00:14:29,550
You don't have it? Oh dear

303
00:14:32,510 --> 00:14:34,348
No, it's not here either

304
00:14:37,748 --> 00:14:41,468
It's not there either, and not here... where did it go?

305
00:14:41,521 --> 00:14:42,575
Where? This is infuriating

306
00:14:52,227 --> 00:14:54,038
Her cries are truly terrifying

307
00:14:54,063 --> 00:14:56,002
She's really giving me a headache

308
00:14:56,037 --> 00:14:58,030
Don't do that, don't cry

309
00:15:06,000 --> 00:15:06,970
Where is it?

310
00:15:09,796 --> 00:15:10,909
Ah, over there

311
00:15:11,703 --> 00:15:13,900
Who on earth is this child?

312
00:15:13,963 --> 00:15:16,900
I think this child must have something special about them

313
00:15:27,133 --> 00:15:28,866
Oh, it's Golden Macaque again?

314
00:15:29,725 --> 00:15:32,152
Little Sprite, I must defeat you today.

315
00:15:32,204 --> 00:15:33,900
Oh no, Golden Macaque, don't fight.

316
00:15:33,951 --> 00:15:35,293
Don't be noisy, Little Sprite.

317
00:15:35,344 --> 00:15:36,986
If you don't want Jian Zai to get hurt,

318
00:15:37,037 --> 00:15:38,560
then hurry up and compete with me.

319
00:15:40,850 --> 00:15:42,450
Who is it? Come out.

320
00:15:44,802 --> 00:15:46,042
Oh no, Little Ling Lung?

321
00:15:46,355 --> 00:15:47,609
Little Ling Lung...

322
00:15:47,660 --> 00:15:48,814
Hey, it's Poodle?

323
00:15:48,865 --> 00:15:50,982
Hey, brother, let me help you

324
00:15:51,398 --> 00:15:53,217
Oh, the little demon's child is here?

325
00:15:53,268 --> 00:15:55,678
That's right, I am the little demon's child

326
00:15:55,729 --> 00:15:58,015
Oh my, is that the little demon's child?

327
00:15:59,700 --> 00:16:01,032
Now let me help my brother

328
00:16:01,083 --> 00:16:02,520
I'm going to take you down

329
00:16:03,833 --> 00:16:05,377
It's just a petty trick

330
00:16:05,427 --> 00:16:08,136
Oh my, it turns out to be a dart made of bamboo?

331
00:16:08,187 --> 00:16:09,504
I'm not a formal ninja

332
00:16:09,554 --> 00:16:11,569
So I can't carry lethal darts

333
00:16:11,620 --> 00:16:15,040
Alright, let me show you the awesome skills of a true ninja.

334
00:16:20,563 --> 00:16:22,960
How are you? Are you okay?

335
00:16:23,682 --> 00:16:24,760
Let me deal with him.

336
00:16:24,937 --> 00:16:27,402
Brother, let me defeat him by myself.

337
00:16:27,453 --> 00:16:29,532
Huh, I didn't expect this kid to be so boastful.

338
00:16:29,583 --> 00:16:31,582
We haven't decided the winner yet.

339
00:16:33,455 --> 00:16:36,064
That's all... hurry up and cry...

340
00:16:36,115 --> 00:16:38,640
What now? Do you know how formidable the Kōka school is now?

341
00:16:38,730 --> 00:16:39,880
Damn it.

342
00:16:40,650 --> 00:16:42,480
Do you know how formidable I am?

343
00:16:51,189 --> 00:16:54,010
Ouch... My head feels like it's about to split open from you shaking it

344
00:16:54,061 --> 00:16:55,130
Ouch, what's wrong?

345
00:16:55,181 --> 00:16:57,651
My weapon is powerful, isn't it? Surrender yet?

346
00:16:57,702 --> 00:16:59,983
I surrender, I surrender

347
00:17:01,403 --> 00:17:03,221
Your secret weapon is really powerful

348
00:17:03,272 --> 00:17:04,770
Compared to my brother's kung fu

349
00:17:04,828 --> 00:17:06,970
It's really a small thing compared to a big one

350
00:17:07,123 --> 00:17:08,946
Jian Zai, let me introduce you

351
00:17:08,997 --> 00:17:11,080
This is my little one, his name is...

352
00:17:12,890 --> 00:17:15,790
Of course, if you cry, you'll faint from crying

353
00:17:20,511 --> 00:17:23,174
Oh, so it’s the little sprite’s kid?

354
00:17:23,237 --> 00:17:25,406
I knew there was a connection a long time ago

355
00:17:25,457 --> 00:17:27,795
Let’s keep him here, okay?

356
00:17:27,846 --> 00:17:29,920
Our family has now become five people

357
00:17:30,284 --> 00:17:32,454
Sigh, this is going to be really lively

358
00:17:34,587 --> 00:17:37,041
Mom, where did you go?

359
00:17:37,099 --> 00:17:39,080
Why did you leave me like this?

360
00:17:42,068 --> 00:17:44,720
Oh no, he’s about to cry out

361
00:17:45,580 --> 00:17:47,582
Don’t let him cry at all

362
00:17:47,633 --> 00:17:49,116
Quickly change the channel

363
00:17:49,167 --> 00:17:50,960
Oh no, I have to change it again

364
00:17:51,081 --> 00:17:52,286
Here it comes

365
00:17:52,337 --> 00:17:54,237
Oh no, Mummy, don't die

366
00:17:54,288 --> 00:17:56,560
Don't leave us behind

367
00:17:57,686 --> 00:17:59,087
Who says I'm stupid?

368
00:17:59,138 --> 00:18:00,653
I say you're stupider than a roasted goose

369
00:18:00,704 --> 00:18:01,793
Are you that clever?

370
00:18:01,844 --> 00:18:03,185
Who's cooler than me?

371
00:18:03,210 --> 00:18:04,050
How are you cooler? Tell me quickly!

372
00:18:04,210 --> 00:18:05,428
I'm the coolest, you're stupid!

373
00:18:05,452 --> 00:18:07,056
You haven't seen it? Awesome!

374
00:18:07,081 --> 00:18:08,463
Are you that capable?

375
00:18:12,877 --> 00:18:15,737
It's going to be troublesome after Xiao Linglong arrives.

